	<title>Visit</title>
</head>
<body style="padding: 15px;">
	<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-secondary shadow-lg p-3 mb-5 rounded">
		  <a class="navbar-brand" href="localhost:4567">Barber shop</a>
		  <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNavDropdown" aria-controls="navbarNavDropdown" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
		    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
		  </button>
		  <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNavDropdown">
		    <ul class="navbar-nav">
		      <li class="nav-item active">
		        <a class="nav-link" href="/">Home <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
		      </li>
		      <li class="nav-item">
		        <a class="nav-link" href="/about">About</a>
		      </li>
		      <li class="nav-item">
		        <a class="nav-link" href="/visit">Visit</a>
		      </li>
		    </ul>
		  </div>
		</nav>		
	<div>
		<h1><center>Welcome to Barber shop!</center></h1>
			<center>We are open</center>
	</div>		

	<p><b>Заполняйте снизу анкету и приходите к нам⬇️.</b></p>


	<form action="/visit" method="POST">
		<div class="form-group">
		<p>
			<h3>Name:</h3>
			<input type="text" class="form-control border border-success" name="username" placeholder="name" />
		</p>
		</div>

		<div class="form-group">
		<p>
			<h3>Phone:</h3> 
			<input type="text" class="form-control border border-success" name="phone" placeholder="phone" />
		</p>
		</div>

		<div class="form-group">
		<p>
			<h3>Date and Time:</h3>
			<input type="text" class="form-control border border-success" name="datetime" placeholder="date and time" />
		</p>
		</div>

		<div class="form-group">
		<h3><p>Your hairdresser</p></h3>
		<select class="form-control border border-success" name="barber">
			<option>-=Не выбрано=-</option>
      		<option>Vova</option>
      		<option>Karina</option>
      		<option>Misha</option>
      		<option>Artem</option>
      		<option>Anya</option>
    	</select>
    	</div>


    	<h3><p>Color:</p></h3>
		<select id="color">
		  <option value="#7bd148">Green</option>
		  <option value="#5484ed">Bold blue</option>
		  <option value="#a4bdfc">Blue</option>
		  <option value="#46d6db">Turquoise</option>
		  <option value="#7ae7bf">Light green</option>
		  <option value="#51b749">Bold green</option>
		  <option value="#fbd75b">Yellow</option>
		  <option value="#ffb878">Orange</option>
		  <option value="#ff887c">Red</option>
		  <option value="#dc2127">Bold red</option>
		  <option value="#dbadff">Purple</option>
		  <option value="#e1e1e1">Gray</option>
		</select>

		<p>
			<input type="submit" class="btn btn-info" />
		</p>

		<script type="text/javascript">
		$('#color').simplecolorpicker();
		</script>
	</form>



</body>
</html>